            , were indicted, <rs id="t17790915-13-off71" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17790915-13-off71" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790915-13-off71" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               the first for the wilful murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17790915-13-victim189" type="victimName">
                           Thomas
                            Hughes
                        <interp inst="t17790915-13-victim189" type="surname" value="Hughes"></interp>
