                     <interp inst="t17790915-13-verdict73" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790915-13-verdict73" type="verdictSubcategory" value="manslaughter"></interp>
               Not Guilty of murder, but Guilty of Manslaughter only
            </rs>.</p>
